x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"277\"><p data-block-id=\"783f9060-f315-483c-b020-37f8079c7e5f\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"width:278px;\"><p data-block-id=\"cf665411-2c95-4a5d-b9e9-0d3ec39cf64a\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"277\"><p data-block-id=\"55cbaf83-ec18-4147-8950-585e0c4aaba7\"><strong>การคืนเงินบางส่วนหลายครั้ง</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"width:278px;\"><p data-block-id=\"957d2006-c589-4751-a1a0-174321a498e2\">&#x274c;</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"277\"><p data-block-id=\"3795b679-c38a-4fae-88f4-7a3498c5b08e\"><strong>ความถูกต้องของการคืนเงิน</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"width:278px;\"><p data-block-id=\"9f5634ea-ac19-47ae-9a88-b4b2d4a3d107\">N/A</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"277\"><p data-block-id=\"d1760170-fa28-4c8b-b533-419100be3192\"><strong>การผสานรวมที่เข้ากันได้</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"278\" style=\"width:278px;\"><p data-block-id=\"60823a34-d1b1-427e-90ab-60a877255f19\">Payment API, Payment Links</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"aca3a1ec-7734-4769-ad67-b377d9c2bdd1\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"7cacbff0-6097-4577-8bea-2670eefceb05\"></h2><p data-block-id=\"3a86b5ec-38da-4400-83d2-ef1024cbe6c9\"></p><p data-block-id=\"12295416-ce37-4b1f-ae9c-e422707d5254\"></p><p data-block-id=\"8e9aac87-b7ff-4f0e-b9c9-0178d8f76e42\"></p><p data-block-id=\"1fba7422-3f0f-475f-a3cd-ed72e33bce4f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"acd97665-43b1-498b-89ca-e66b24c0a68f\"></p><p data-block-id=\"490a489a-2a58-4dc9-96ea-9e5cc09fc8be\"></p>","SeoTitle":"BDO การหักบัญชีโดยตรง","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"BDO Direct Debit","Slug":"bdo-direct-debit","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"b1040702-ed6c-4864-84ff-67a01ba05fef\"><img data-block-id=\"ba18f3c-08bc-4a1b-b04a-ad3d40fabef1\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/BDO_Unibank_(logo).svg.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"249\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:249px;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"4211693a-308c-4068-9616-3e68df2e0e78\">BDO Unibank, el banco más grande de Filipinas, ofrece BDO ePayment, una solución de Pago en línea segura diseñada para simplificar las Transacciones tanto para Comercios como para Clientes. Este servicio permite a los Clientes realizar Pagos directamente desde sus Cuentas de BDO durante las compras en línea.</p><p data-block-id=\"d8636ee0-ede8-4af2-92b6-2311adbc4ee9\">Para los Comercios, ofrecer BDO ePayment permite una integración fluida de los Pagos bancarios en el proceso de pago (checkout), lo que aumenta la confianza del Cliente y amplía las opciones de Pago.</p><hr class=\"hr-divider1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"6146dcc6-4245-4158-a034-de0971f8c50b\">Características</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"878\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:878px;width:878px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:300px;\"><col style=\"width:578px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"300\" style=\"background-color:#f2f2f2;\"><p><strong>Código de Channel</strong></p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"578\"><p><span s